      <title>美国石油供应商切入OPEC+主导的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/us-oil-suppliers-cut-into-markets-dominated-by-opec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自西方国家于 2022 年开始对俄罗斯实施制裁以来，美国石油供应商已强行进入曾经由 OPEC 及其盟友主导的市场，创下了五个新的月度出口记录。安东尼·迪保拉 (Anthony DiPaola) 接受彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/us-oil-suppliers-cut-into-markets-dominated-by-opec</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 10:25:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对派获胜后土耳其建筑公司暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/turkish-construction-firms-tumble-after-opposition-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其执政党在市政选举中遭遇前所未有的失败，导致政府支持的大型项目实现的可能性降低，周一伊斯坦布尔的建筑公司股价大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/turkish-construction-firms-tumble-after-opposition-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 10:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求下滑后巴基斯坦通胀降至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-a-third-month-as-high-rates-hit-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于创纪录的借贷成本削弱了经济增长和国内需求，巴基斯坦3月份的通胀率连续第三个月放缓至近两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/pakistan-inflation-eases-a-third-month-as-high-rates-hit-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 09:13:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
